105
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:26,380
Rym: Everything in your computer plugs into the motherboard.

106
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:30,000
Rym: Every component of your computer communicates with other components through the motherboard.

107
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:34,560
